       This program uses TextEditor.mcc, (c) 1997 by Allan Odgaard
                     http://www.DIKU.dk/students/duff/

 TextEditor.mcc is a fast multiline stringgadget, made as a customclass
                         for @{"MagicUserInterface" Link MUI}.
