@NODE "register" "How to register"
@TOC "MAIN"

                              Registration

   If  You  think this program is worth using then You should register.
 This  costs only US$ 3 or 10 PLN so please consider it. There are many
 advantages of being a registered user:

 + You'll get rid of that annoying requester.
 + You'll have the right to free updates of this program.
 + You support programmers and the Amiga.
 + You'll be able to save configuration of HTML Editor.

  So  if You want to register this program then send US$ 3 or 10 PLN to
 the  @{"author" LINK "author"}  with  a  registration form (see below).  As for now I can
 only  accept money sent in letter but I'm working on ability to accept
 credit cards (VISA, MasterCard, EuroCard etc.) so if You have one then
 contact  me  (by  e-mail)  to know if I can accept it.  If You live in
 Poland then You can of course send the money in postal order.

 Unfortunatly I can only send registered copies by e-mail.

 Please fill in this registration form.  If You wont, You wont get Your
 registered copy.

